data.description: The BROOKDALE III G in Belvedere Place community offers a 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom, open and split design. This home sits on a spacious corner lot with large gate access. Upgrades include luxury vinyl plank flooring, blinds throughout, stainless gas appliance package, under-mount kitchen sink, LED lighting packages, and more! Special Features: double vanity and walk-in closet in the master suite, walk-in closets in bedrooms 2 and 3, covered rear porch, granite countertops, ceiling fans in the living room and master bedroom, double insulation in the attic r38 rating, handicap modifications, security system, Honeywell Smart Connect WiFi thermostat, Venetian bronze fixtures, smoke and carbon monoxide detectors, insulated garage door with 2 remotes, seasonal landscaping package, fenced yard, gutters, 30-year shingles, 8x10 shed, and SOLAR PANELS! Energy Efficient Features: tankless gas water heater, Frigidaire stainless steel appliance package, vinyl low E tilt-in windows, radiant barrier roof decking, and more!
